	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cum tuo me nomine pridie salutaret <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p506" cert="high">Butlerus</persName> noster et anxie te cupere de rebus <placeName type="citizen_name" cert="high" ref="l303">Madenburgensibus</placeName>, quonam modo accidissent, mihi significaret, forte fortuna cuidam ex amicis allatus est e <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l361" cert="high">Norimberga</placeName> libellus <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l303" cert="high">Madenburgi</placeName> aeditus, ex quo omnia intelliges.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Miram de se constantiae expectationem omnium animis incutit illa urbs, quam utinam et vicinae imitarentur!</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De plusculis enim ambigitur, mansuraene in fide Christi sint necne, usque adeo in speciem quidem plausibilibus, sed longe tamen insidiosissimis artibus tentantur quaedam, quas speramus tamen circumspectius acturas esse, quam vulgus sibi polliceatur.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Interea temporis nihil habemus ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l18" cert="high">Augusta</placeName> certi, nisi quod certo ferunt <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18538" cert="high">Caesarem</persName> filio suo <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18575" cert="high">Philippo</persName> fratris <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18477" cert="high">Ferdinandi</persName> filiam uxorem daturum magno quidem fratris consensu, pro lege videlicet caninae verecundiae.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si quid acciderit, brevi intelliges.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l473" cert="high">Sangalli</placeName> 23. octobris anno 50.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8049" cert="high">Ioachimus Vadianus</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Domino <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Henrycho Bullingero</persName>, praeclarae urbis <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tigurinae</placeName> episcopo, domino suo inprimis colendo.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
